&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova light,arial nova light_embeddedfont,arial nova light_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Analysis was conducted on the firearm recovered during the initial arrest and the casings found at the scene. As a result of this analysis, the additional charges of unlawful use of a weapon and criminal mischief are being filed against Alexander Salgado-Maya.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova light,arial nova light_embeddedfont,arial nova light_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

