&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to Report a Wildlife and/or Habitat Law Violation or Suspicious Activity: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;TIP Hotline: 1-800-452-7888 or *OSP (*677)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;TIP email: &lt;a href="mailto:TIP@osp.oregon.gov"&gt;TIP@osp.oregon.gov&lt;/a&gt; (monitored Monday through Friday 8 a.m. to 5 p.m.)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For more information, visit the Oregon State Police &lt;a href="https://gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oregon.gov%2Fosp%2Fprograms%2Ffw%2FPages%2Ftip.aspx&amp;amp;data=05%7C02%7COSP.OSPPIO%40osp.oregon.gov%7Cf0a97e47156c4070c8fb08de0784a69d%7C776738eb4f9b444fbc334dd4e8e1a9b5%7C0%7C0%7C638956463480340070%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;amp;sdata=TcMJpBv3u7QSr8tp67F%2BkSvBb4J7fJi8VRkQykFd60Q%3D&amp;amp;reserved=0"&gt;Turn-in-Poachers (TIP) web page&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;# # #&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Oregon State Police&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Oregon State Police (OSP) is a multidisciplinary organization charged with protecting the people, wildlife, and natural resources in Oregon. OSP enforces traffic laws on the state&rsquo;s roadways, investigates and solves crime, conducts postmortem examinations and forensic analysis, and provides background checks, and law enforcement data. The agency regulates gaming and enforces fish, wildlife, and natural resource laws. OSP is comprised of more than 1,400 staff members &ndash; including troopers, investigators, and professional staff &ndash; who provide a full range of policing and public safety services to Oregon and to other law enforcement agencies throughout the state.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&ldquo;Everything Is About to Change for Oregon&rsquo;s Food System&rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As SNAP Cuts Loom, CAFE Rallies Community Funders to Strengthen Local Food Equity&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PORTLAND, OR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; &mdash; In the coming weeks, more than &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;300,000 Oregonians&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; will receive notices that their &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SNAP (Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; benefits are changing, reducing the amount of food many households can afford. According to the Oregon Department of Human Services, these federal changes will impact families, older adults, and individuals across every county.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;At the same time, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;cuts to the USDA programs like the Local Food Purchase Assistance (LFPA)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; program have sharply reduced the supply of fresh food flowing into Oregon&rsquo;s emergency food network. The dual blow underscores a critical truth: the safety nets families rely on are fraying, and local community systems must step in to fill the gap.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;That&rsquo;s where the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coalition for Advancing Food Equity (CAFE)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; comes in. Formed by a collective of Oregon-based food security organizations, CAFE&rsquo;s mission is to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;strengthen food equity through shared systems, collaborative operations, and policy solutions &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;that stretch resources and get nutritious food to those who need it most.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rebuilding What&rsquo;s Broken &mdash; Together&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;Leading this work is a creative &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;collaborative funding model&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; made possible by the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Zidell Family Foundation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;, which helped rally the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marie Lamfrom Foundation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; and the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Harbourton Foundation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; to launch CAFE&rsquo;s first shared bulk purchasing and distribution project. The initiative allows member organizations to pool funds, purchase food at scale, and share labor to reduce duplication and costs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&ldquo;We believe in the power of collaboration over competition,&rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;said &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Charlene Zidell&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;, Director of the Zidell Family Foundation and lead organizer of the CAFE Funder Circle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&ldquo;By pooling resources and aligning around shared goals, we can protect our neighbors from the worst of these cuts and build stronger local systems for the future.&rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&ldquo;Marie Lamfrom Foundation invests in communities that care for one another, and that&rsquo;s exactly what this collaboration represents,&rdquo; said &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tyler Hobbs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;, President of the Marie Lamfrom Foundation. &ldquo;When we strengthen local systems and partnerships, we strengthen the dignity and well-being of every Oregonian. Supporting CAFE ensures that more people have access to the fresh, nourishing food they deserve.&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&ldquo;We&rsquo;re proud to support a network of smaller, community-based organizations harnessing their collective strength to meet a shared goal,&rdquo; said &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Carrie Lawliss&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;, Director of the Harbourton Foundation. &ldquo;When local nonprofits come together to coordinate, rather than compete, it creates a powerful ripple effect, and it&rsquo;s critical that we resource that collaboration so it can last.&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Community Voices: The Human Impact&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;For the people CAFE partners serve, these changes aren&rsquo;t abstract&mdash;they&rsquo;re deeply personal.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&ldquo;I&rsquo;m sure you are aware of the big changes that are going on in the government,&rdquo; said a Lift UP client who lives in affordable housing supported through the coalition. &ldquo;We have been put against the wall because every day we have less and less benefits. With your service, it has been lifesaving&mdash;it&rsquo;s like being in the middle of the ocean and someone throws you a lifesaver.&rdquo; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;Because food is so expensive, without Lift UP I wouldn&rsquo;t be able to afford to eat. I received about $60 from food stamps, but my groceries cost almost $700 last month. Lift UP helps me feed my grandkids when they come to visit.&rdquo; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coalition Leaders Speak Out&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&ldquo;We&rsquo;re already seeing demand spike across our pantries,&rdquo; said &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stephanie Barr&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;, Executive Director of Lift Urban Portland and Coalition Lead Spokesperson. &ldquo;CAFE&rsquo;s model gives us an exciting path forward&mdash; it allows us to get better deals, coordinate distributions, maximize efficiency, and lean into our strengths so we can focus on what matters most: feeding people with dignity.&rdquo; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&ldquo;Getting fresh fruit into the hands of people who need it shouldn&rsquo;t be a struggle,&rdquo; added &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Heather Keisler Fornes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;, Executive Director of Portland Fruit Tree Project. &ldquo;Through CAFE, we can scale our gleaning work, coordinate harvests, and inject more fresh produce into community pantries even as federal supplies decline.&rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&ldquo;When food systems are stressed, the organizations that distribute food are often pushed to the brink,&rdquo; said &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Graham Craft&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; of William Temple House. &ldquo;CAFE gives us a structure for resilience, so one organization&rsquo;s burden doesn&rsquo;t collapse the whole network.&rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CAFE is Collaborating with City Leadership for Portland Specific Solutions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&ldquo;The Oregon Department of Human Services recently announced that SNAP benefits, which are fully funded by the USDA, will end after October 31st as a result of the government shutdown. Let's be honest -- if SNAP is defunded, over 750,000 Oregonians risk acute and immediate hunger. This is an unacceptable burden for working-class households to endure. In response, local organizations have come together through CAFE to strengthen food supply systems and ensure food reaches our communities. This collaboration will inform a long-term vision for improving affordability, access, and quality in Oregon&rsquo;s food programs, including exploring future municipal grocery models that remove barriers in our neighborhoods.&rdquo; - the office of City Council Member Mitch Greene.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ripple Effects Beyond Food&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;The SNAP reductions are expected to impact other household essentials. Families facing food shortages often delay paying utility bills or medical costs, creating a cascading effect across Oregon&rsquo;s health and housing systems. The loss of USDA funding compounds that pressure, particularly for fresh fruits and vegetables that once flowed through local purchasing programs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How Oregonians Can Help&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;CAFE urges individuals and businesses to take action now:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; position: relative; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;
     &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Donate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; to strengthen local food purchasing and distribution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
     &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; position: relative; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;
     &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Volunteer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; with coalition partners to support gleaning, packing, and delivery efforts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
     &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW166386916 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; position: relative; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;
     &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advocate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; by signing up for Oregon Food Bank&rsquo;s &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Action Alerts&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt; to stay informed on upcoming legislation and policy changes:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:wordvisicarriagereturn_msfontservice,helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
     &lt;span style="color:rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW166386916 BCX0" href="https://secure.oregonfoodbank.org/a/action-alert-sign-up" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;https://secure.oregonfoodbank.org/a/action-alert-sign-up&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family:helvetica neue,helvetica neue_embeddedfont,helvetica neue_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:9.5pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
     &lt;/li&gt;
