&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;For additional information about the investigation of the &lt;em&gt;E. coli&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;infections, see the Washington State Department of Health&rsquo;s &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW8845741 BCX8" href="https://doh.wa.gov/you-and-your-family/illness-and-disease-z/foodborne-illness/outbreaks/2025-outbreak-shiga-toxin-producing-e-coli-stec-infections-linked-twin-sisters-creamery-aged-raw" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;announcement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:14pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

