&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px"&gt;About Capitol Auto Group:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px"&gt;For more than &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12px"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;98 years&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px"&gt;, Capitol Auto Group has proudly served the Greater Salem, Oregon area. The group includes five dealerships: Capitol Toyota, Capitol Subaru, Capitol Chevrolet/Cadillac and Capitol Nissan, plus Capitol Collision Center. For the past 14 years, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Automotive News&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px"&gt; has recognized the company among the nation&rsquo;s &ldquo;Top 150 Best Dealerships to Work For in America.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

