&lt;p&gt;If you need help with these or other related services, please contact Stella Rausch-Scott at 503-490-3717 (voice/text) or&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="mailto:stella.m.rausch-scott@oha.oregon.gov" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; color: rgb(6, 66, 118);"&gt;stella.m.rausch-scott@oha.oregon.gov&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;at least 48 business hours before the meeting.&lt;/p&gt;

