&lt;p&gt;&lt;big&gt;&lt;span class="marker"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;Derek Thompson, co-author of Abundance, will deliver a keynote address exploring practical actions that could help Cascadia overcome economic headwinds and harness its strengths to build housing and seize other opportunities &mdash; making his perspective especially timely as the region charts its future.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/big&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
