&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;As Deputy Fire Marshal, Jason looks forward to combining his operational experience with his passion for prevention and education. &ldquo;I enjoy being out in the community and building positive relationships with the public. A significant part of this position centers on education, which closely reflects the work I&rsquo;ve done throughout my career. I&rsquo;ve seen firsthand how fire safety practices save lives and prevent serious injuries. Being able to share that knowledge with others will be both meaningful and rewarding.&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
