&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#000080"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11:10 AM &ndash; 12:10 PM | Ed Edmo Storytelling &amp;amp; Meet-and-Greet&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;Listen to local legend and Shoshone-Bannock leader &lt;strong&gt;Ed Edmo&lt;/strong&gt; share his captivating poetry and stories of the Pacific Northwest. Edmo is one of the faces of the &lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW110068027 BCX0" href="https://portofportland.com/communitymural" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(70, 120, 134)"&gt;A Place Called Home mura&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;l at the PDX Airport. Afterwards, say hello and have your book of his poetry personally signed by him!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#000080"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12:20 PM &ndash; 1:20 PM | Wen&rsquo;&iacute;pt (Songs) &ndash; Indigenous Contemporary Jazz Combo&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW110068027 BCX0" href="https://www.instagram.com/wenipt/" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wen&rsquo;&iacute;pt&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;is an Indigenous-led contemporary jazz group that celebrates Native artistry through music and storytelling, honoring the long tradition of Indigenous musicians in jazz.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;span style="color:#000080"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12:00 PM &ndash; 2:00 PM | Cultural Demos with Whitney Jackson&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(21, 61, 99)"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;Traveling from the &lt;strong&gt;Warm Springs Reservation,&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Whitney Jackson&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;span style="color:rgb(8, 8, 9)"&gt;W&iacute;laps Ayat&lt;/span&gt; / &lt;em&gt;Sturgeon Woman&lt;/em&gt;) will share her deep knowledge of traditional lifeways along the Columbia River &mdash; from fishing for salmon and sturgeon to preserving traditional foods. She&rsquo;ll show her &lt;strong&gt;award-winning wind-dried salmon and eel&lt;/strong&gt; and&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt; shar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt; about &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt;her&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt; work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt;teac&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt;h&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt;ing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt; and revitaliz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt;ing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="background-color:var(--clrCommentsHighlightRest,rgba(209,209,209,.5))"&gt; the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Ichishk&iacute;in&lt;/strong&gt; language at the Warm Springs Language School.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#000080"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1:00 PM &ndash; 3:00 PM | Cultural Demos with Becca Lynn&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Becca Lynn&lt;/strong&gt;, granddaughter of the founder of the &lt;strong&gt;Miss Indian Northwest Pageant&lt;/strong&gt; and current Executive Director of the program, is a dedicated community leader and talented regalia artist. She&rsquo;ll share about her work with &lt;strong&gt;Miss Indian Northwest&lt;/strong&gt; and showcase her beautiful beadwork and regalia.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

