&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kimberly Smart, &lt;/strong&gt;founder of the &lt;strong&gt;Missing Murdered Indigenous Women (MMIW) Search and Hope Alliance&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW110068027 BCX0" href="https://www.statesmanjournal.com/story/news/local/oregon/2025/03/03/oregon-legislature-missing-murdered-indigenous-people-oregon-health-authority/80753886007/" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(70, 120, 134)"&gt;leader of national advocacy efforts,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; will share about awareness, action, and healing for the Missing and Murdered Indigenous Women movement, honoring families and strengthening community action.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW110068027 BCX0" style="font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#000080"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1:30 PM &ndash; 3:30 PM | Turquoise Pride &ndash; Local Native Drum Group&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
