&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SALEM, Ore. &mdash; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;A coordinated retail theft operation conducted Thursday at the Willamette Town Center resulted in multiple arrests and the recovery of stolen merchandise.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
