&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:cambria,serif; font-size:12pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW263903301 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;SALEM, Oregon&mdash;The Oregon State Parks and Recreation Commission will convene Nov. 19 for a virtual meeting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW263903301 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Commissioners will convene an executive session at 8:30 a.m. virtually to discuss acquisition priorities and opportunities, and potential litigation. The Executive Session will be held pursuant to ORS 192.660(2)(e) and (h) and is closed to the public.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW263903301 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;A business meeting will begin at 9:45 a.m. virtually and will be open to the public.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW263903301 BCX0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; overflow: visible; cursor: text; clear: both; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;Anyone may attend or listen to the business meeting; instructions on how to listen will be posted on the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW263903301 BCX0" href="https://www.oregon.gov/oprd/CAC/Pages/CAC-oprc.aspx" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;commission web page&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt; prior to the meeting. The business meeting includes time for informal public comment related to any items not on the agenda.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:whitney book,whitney book_embeddedfont,whitney book_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

