&lt;p style="text-align:center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Triple your impact: Pacific Power will match your contribution to Oregon Energy Fund 2-for-1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
