&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Pacific Power provides safe and reliable electric service to more than&amp;nbsp;800,000&amp;nbsp;customers&amp;nbsp;in Oregon,&amp;nbsp;Washington&amp;nbsp;and California&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;The company&amp;nbsp;supplies customers with&amp;nbsp;electricity from a diverse portfolio of generating plants including hydroelectric, natural gas, coal, wind, geothermal and solar resources. Pacific Power is part of PacifiCorp, one of the lowest-cost electricity producers in the United States, with&amp;nbsp;over&amp;nbsp;two&amp;nbsp;million customers in six western states. For more information, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW36182844 BCX8" href="https://www.pacificpower.net/" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;PacificPower.net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
