&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;In his new role, Fitzwater will oversee emergency operations, staffing coordination, and resource planning &mdash; work that will help guide the District as it continues to meet the needs of a growing community.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
