&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Salem temporarily suspends downtown paid on-street parking Saturday, Nov. 29&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;Free on-street parking downtown from 8 a.m. - 8 p.m. on Sat., Nov. 29&lt;/li&gt;
