&lt;p&gt;&middot; The Al Angelo Company - 400 E. Mill Plain Blvd., Suite 500&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&middot; Vancouver City Hall - 415 W. 6th St.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&middot; Vancouver Fire Department Station 5 &ndash; 7110 N.E. 63rd St.&lt;/p&gt;

