&lt;p&gt;Shop local while giving: Purchasing gifts from local retailers helps keep dollars in Vancouver&rsquo;s economy, supporting local jobs and services. Community members are encouraged to buy toys for donation from local businesses like Kazoodles Toys &amp;amp; Gifts, 13503 S.E. Mill Plain Blvd. (or &lt;a href="https://kazoodlestoys.com/"&gt;order online&lt;/a&gt;) and Lyon and Pearle, 607 Washington Street (or &lt;a href="https://lyonandpearle.com/"&gt;order online&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;br /&gt;
