&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align:center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:20px"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Portland Metro Chamber Recognizes Jordan Schnitzer and Albina Vision Trust for Outstanding Achievements at Annual Business Leadership Evening&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:18px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;With elected leaders in attendance, the William S. Naito Outstanding Service Award and the President&rsquo;s Award was bestowed to business community leaders&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face="wordvisicarriagereturn_msfontservice, aptos, aptos_embeddedfont, aptos_msfontservice, sans-serif"&gt;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://portlandbusinessalliance.sharepoint.com/:f:/s/all-alliance-team/EiCOwzV4SadGnjoFSiJ-HQsBOCiksIKSI7N4JmtKr0Hnow?e=F1t3E2"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;Link to Photos and Videos of Event, Speakers, and Awardees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PORTLAND, OR&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&mdash;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nov. 12, 2025 &mdash;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;The Portland Metro Chamber brought together the region&rsquo;s business community yesterday evening for one of its most anticipated annual events&mdash;the 2025 Business Leadership Evening. More than 550 industry professionals and elected officials gathered at the Portland Art Museum to celebrate exceptional leaders whose contributions to business, philanthropy, and civic engagement strengthen the fabric of the Rose City. At a time when the region faces economic headwinds, the event underscored what can be achieved when the community unites around shared values and a common vision for progress.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speakers included U.S. Senator Jeff Merkley, former State Senator Betsy Johnson, Chamber President and CEO Andrew Hoan, and honoree Jordan D. Schnitzer.&lt;/strong&gt; They highlighted how the resilience and creativity of Portlanders has shined especially bright recently in the face of federal and local challenges. They also emphasized the integral role of business leadership in driving innovation, fostering collaboration, and building&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;strong and inclusive Portland economy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;The Chamber bestowed the &lt;strong&gt;William S. Naito Outstanding Service Award &lt;/strong&gt;to Jordan D. Schnitzer. In honor of the late Bill Naito, the award recognizes Schnitzer&rsquo;s decades of visionary leadership in building one of the West Coast&rsquo;s most successful commercial real estate portfolios and driving regional economic growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Schnitzer&rsquo;s journey began in 1965&mdash;Jordan, Harold and Arlene Schnitzer&rsquo;s son, began working weekends and evenings performing maintenance and janitorial duties in the family&rsquo;s apartment, retail and office buildings. After graduating from the University of Oregon and Lewis &amp;amp; Clark Law School, Jordan joined the family business full-time in 1976.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;By 1995, Jordan Schnitzer assumed the role of President and CEO of what is known today as Schnitzer Properties, growing the company&rsquo;s commercial real estate holdings from 3.4 million square feet to 31 million square feet across six Western states by 2025.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Jordan combined his father&rsquo;s love for smaller-unit buildings like apartments and offices with his interest in flex industrial warehouse spaces to carve out a visionary niche for industrial workspaces for small and mid-sized manufacturers, wholesalers, distributors and service providers&mdash;the backbone of the American economy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Today, the 75-year-old family company owns more than 200 properties with 4,250+ tenants with nearly $500 million of new development underway in 2025. Schnitzer works every day from his office in downtown Portland and lives with his family in Multnomah County.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Beyond his real estate achievements, Schnitzer is an internationally recognized art collector, named by&amp;nbsp;ARTNews as one of the world's top 200 art collectors. The Jordan Schnitzer Family Foundation, with its collection of thousands of contemporary artworks, has organized and funded more than 180 exhibitions at 130 museums at no cost to the museums. Additionally, Schnitzer serves as president of the Harold &amp;amp; Arlene Schnitzer CARE Foundation, which&nbsp;has donated over $300 million to fund hundreds of nonprofit projects.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&ldquo;I'm honored to accept this year&rsquo;s William S. Naito Award. Bill and I served together on several commissions and if there ever was someone that committed his heart and soul to helping improve Portland, it was Bill Naito,&rdquo; &lt;strong&gt;said Schnitzer.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Schnitzer added, &ldquo;I hope I have followed in Bill&rsquo;s footsteps and look forward to continuing to work every day, not only in our real estate business, but philanthropically and civically to make our home, Portland and the State of Oregon, a wonderful place to live.&rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The President&rsquo;s Award&lt;/strong&gt; was presented to Albina Vision Trust (AVT) for its exceptional accomplishments to transform the future of our community&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&mdash;leading the largest restorative redevelopment effort in America.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt; Executive Director Winta Yohannes accepted the award on behalf of AVT.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Once known as the &ldquo;Harlem on the Willamette,&rdquo; the neighborhood of Lower Albina was nationally recognized as a West Coast hotspot for jazz and soul music before urban renewal projects displaced families and dismantled its social and cultural fabric. Albina was classified &ldquo;blighted&rdquo; and redlined, and families were displaced so that the neighborhood could be demolished and replaced by Interstate 5, Veterans Memorial Coliseum, and the Portland Public Schools headquarters facility.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Today, Albina Vision Trust &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;is reclaiming land and creating inclusive opportunities for housing and economic development to rebuild the 94-acre thriving community. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;In 2023, Albina Vision Trust broke ground on the inaugural 94-unit, family-centered affordable housing development, Albina One. In September, the $66.7 million, seven-story apartments opened 94 units of 100% affordable housing,&amp;nbsp;welcoming people back into the district for the first time in 40 years. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Albina Vision Trust is now in the process of acquiring the 10.5-acre Portland Public Schools headquarters campus to deliver 1,000 units of housing for over 3,000 working-class Portlanders, mixed-use commercial space, an education hub for marginalized students, and accessible green spaces.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&ldquo;I am honored to accept this recognition on behalf of the entire Albina Vision Trust team,&rdquo;&lt;strong&gt; said Albina Vision Trust Executive Director Winta Yohannes&lt;/strong&gt;, noting the partnership between the Chamber and AVT. &ldquo;The Portland Metro Chamber was right there cheering on our landmark partnership with the Portland Trailblazers, called the Albina Rose Alliance.&rdquo; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:wordvisicarriagereturn_msfontservice,aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;Yohannes added, &ldquo;Whenever we&rsquo;ve asked PMC to show up in Salem to testify alongside us, they&rsquo;ve never wavered. They&rsquo;ve rolled up their sleeves to join us in coordinating national coalitions for infrastructure investments.&rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;The Portland Metro Chamber is proud to recognize Albina Vision Trust&rsquo;s exceptional leadership in spearheading a nationally heralded, precedent-setting model for 21st century urban restorative development, which has literally and figuratively broken ground to deliver inclusive opportunities for affordable housing and land development, wealth building, and cultural revitalization.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW41722676 BCX0" style="-webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Web&amp;quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:aptos,aptos_embeddedfont,aptos_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;The Chamber is proud to celebrate Jordan Schnitzer and the Albina Vision Trust for their visionary leadership and unwavering commitment to shaping the future of Portland.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a name="_Hlk108004588"&gt;The December quarterly meeting of the Advisory Committee to the Oregon Department of Veterans&rsquo; Affairs (ODVA) will be held virtually and in person on Wednesday, December 3, in the Auditorium of ODVA, located at 700 Summer Street N.E. in Salem. The meeting begins at 9 a.m. and will be followed by a town hall meeting at 11:30 a.m., which is open to the public.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Established in 1945, the Advisory Committee holds a distinct and fundamental role in advising the director and staff of ODVA. The nine members of the Advisory Committee are military veterans from all corners of the state, appointed by the governor to serve and act as advocates for veteran issues and veteran concerns across Oregon.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Following every quarterly business meeting, the committee holds a town hall inviting the public to raise questions or concerns about broad veteran issues or to share information with the committee and agency director.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Members of the community are also invited to submit written public comments to the committee by emailing &lt;a href="mailto:odva_vaac@odva.oregon.gov"&gt;odva_vaac@odva.oregon.gov&lt;/a&gt;. The Advisory Committee meets quarterly on the first Wednesday of March, June, September and December.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REGISTER TO ATTEND&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Please register at &lt;a href="https://events.gcc.teams.microsoft.com/event/b2ce0f46-4c12-4c26-a3a5-d9a9049afbc2@aa3f6932-fa7c-47b4-a0ce-a598cad161cf"&gt;https://events.gcc.teams.microsoft.com/event/b2ce0f46-4c12-4c26-a3a5-d9a9049afbc2@aa3f6932-fa7c-47b4-a0ce-a598cad161cf&lt;/a&gt; to attend the business or town hall portion of this meeting. Attendees will be allowed to participate during the town hall portion only and will be invited to turn on their camera and unmute mics during a recorded meeting that will be posted online at a later date.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Information about the Advisory Committee and meeting materials can be found online at &lt;a href="http://www.oregon.gov/odva/Connect/Pages/Advisory-Committee.aspx"&gt;www.oregon.gov/odva/Connect/Pages/Advisory-Committee.aspx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Established in 1945, the Oregon Department of Veterans&rsquo; Affairs is dedicated to serving Oregon&rsquo;s diverse veteran community that spans five eras of service members. ODVA administers programs and provides special advocacy and assistance in accessing earned veteran benefits across the state. Learn about veteran benefits and services, or locate a local county or Tribal veteran services office online at &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Foregon.gov%2Fodva&amp;amp;data=05%7C01%7CTyler.FRANCKE%40odva.oregon.gov%7C2e0e66d8a3bd4b7f764608da5f8ee76a%7Caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7C0%7C0%7C637927364611703234%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;amp;sdata=2v0CAWb1u5y8%2BPyDDaGs1Cmpv%2BLsgBcCCohVSlSoFXw%3D&amp;amp;reserved=0"&gt;&lt;em&gt;oregon.gov/odva&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;u&gt;. &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;###&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An Oregon Department of Corrections (DOC) adult in custody, Philip Charles Bradley, died the morning of November 13, 2025. Bradley was incarcerated at Oregon State Penitentiary (OSP) in Salem and passed away at the institution. As with all in-custody deaths, the Oregon State Police have been notified, and the State Medical Examiner will determine cause of death.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Bradley entered DOC custody on May 18, 2022, from Multnomah County with an earliest release date of September 26, 2029. Bradley was 46 years old. Next of kin has been notified.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;DOC takes all in-custody deaths seriously. The agency is responsible for the care and custody of approximately 12,000 men and women who are incarcerated in 12 institutions across the state. While crime information is public record, DOC elects to disclose only upon request out of respect for any family or victims.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;OSP is a multi-custody prison located in Salem. Additional information about the Oregon Department of Corrections can be found at &lt;a href="http://www.oregon.gov/doc"&gt;www.oregon.gov/doc&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

