&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11pt"&gt;At 12:05 a.m., the Vancouver Fire Department responded to a fire at the Sterling Heights Apartments located at 1221 SE Ellsworth Drive.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11pt"&gt;Fire crews arrived to find fire coming from one apartment with the sprinkler system activated. Firefighters quickly extinguished the fire and kept it contained to the single unit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11pt"&gt;One occupant was displaced, and no injuries were reported.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11pt"&gt;The Vancouver Fire Marshal&rsquo;s Office is investigating the cause of the fire.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

