&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:asap,asap_embeddedfont,asap_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;No RSVP or registration is required. For interpretation services or accommodations, please contact the City Manager&rsquo;s office at 360-487-8600 or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class="Hyperlink SCXW40749023 BCX8" href="mailto:cityinfo@cityofvancouver.us" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; -webkit-user-drag: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(5, 99, 193); font-family:asap,asap_embeddedfont,asap_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;cityinfo@cityofvancouver.us&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:asap,asap_embeddedfont,asap_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:asap,asap_embeddedfont,asap_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
